<para>Users have to use <ref refid="classmata_1_1IntAlphabet" kindref="compound">IntAlphabet</ref> instead which provides interface identical to other alphabets and can be used in places where an instance of the abstract class <ref refid="classmata_1_1Alphabet" kindref="compound">Alphabet</ref> is required. </para>
